Source Information
  SUNDIALS library (https://computation.llnl.gov/casc/sundials)

Local Build
  set DIR_SUNDIALS to CMake build directory
  
  to use shared SUNDIALS libraries remove MATH_OBJS and add libraries
  to linker arguments
  
  parallel vector implementation is excluded by default to avoid MPI
  dependency, reimplement
    sundials_nvector_empty()
  and link in before libmpt_sundials.so to use parallel implementation